Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.44,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Who was that, I wonder?}Là ai nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.16,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.58,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Aes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.13,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Aes, that was awesome! \NI thought you couldn't swim?}Aes, tuyệt ghê! Cứ tưởng không biết bơi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.63,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,{Being mistaken for Aes makes me \Nwant to kill people.}Bị nhầm với Aes làm tôi đây bực đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.72,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Oh... Are you Aes's twin...}A... sinh đôi với Aes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.47,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,{Alice, yes. And you're Rouge and Naomi.}Alice, hai người là Rouge và Naomi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:34.12,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,{Aes was saying there were a couple of really \Npretty ladies in the cabin next to ours.}Aes nói có hai quý cô xinh đẹp ở phòng bên cạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.12,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Aes is such a nice kid.}Aes là một đứa trẻ ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.78,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,{But "really pretty" was a bit much.}Nhưng cái xinh đẹp là nói quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.18,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,{You're just a couple of ladies \Nwho aren't ugly.}Chỉ là cặp đôi bình thường không xấu.
