Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.79,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{A couple of ladies...}Không phải là...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.25,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{...who aren't ugly.}một cặp đôi bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:57.62,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{We went all the way to Mars only to \Nturn around and go right back to Earth.}Đi tận đến sao Hoả và về tay trắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:01.06,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{That can't be helped. We have to obey orders.}Chịu thôi. Chúng ta phải nghe lệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:04.63,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{The red figure was on Mars, \Nand not only that,}Tên màu đỏ đang ở Sao Hoả, và không chỉ thế,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.80,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{but a yellow one we didn't have \Non record showed up, too.}lại còn xuất hiện một tên màu vàng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:12.60,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{What are those bastards at Aletheia hiding?}Lũ khốn ở Aletheia đang giấu cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:19.83,Default,Fake Reggie/Mark,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Chào!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.70,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,Noid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.29,Default,Guests,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.66,Default,Guests,0,0,0,,{No way...}Đùa à...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:47.59,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{There's been a murder, apparently.}Nghe nói có vụ giết người.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.96,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{A murder? Someone got killed?}Giết người? Ai đó chết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:52.67,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{The killer is Reggie Avan, age 38.}Hung thủ là Reggie Avan, 38 tuổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.38,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{He's 179 centimeters tall \Nand weighs 68 kilograms.}Cao 1m79 và nặng 68kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.98,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{A blond-haired Caucasian man. Still at large.}Một người đàn ông da trắng tóc vàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:03.67,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Passengers have been advised not to leave \Ntheir cabins until the situation is deemed safe.}Hành khách được khuyên không nên rời khỏi phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.20,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Uh... What do we do?}Chúng ta làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.56,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{No choice.}Chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.63,Default,Reggie,0,0,0,,{Let me go! What is it you think I've done?!}Thả ra! Tôi đã làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.99,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,Reggie Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:20.25,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{You're under arrest as the suspected \Nmurderer of Mark Johnson.}Ông bị bắt vì tình nghi giết Mark Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.53,Default,Reggie,0,0,0,,{What? Mark is dead?}Hả? Mark chết rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.09,Default,Reggie,0,0,0,,{No...}Đùa à...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.59,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Because }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ killed him.}Ông giết chứ ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.42,Default,Reggie,0,0,0,,{Why would I have to kill him?!}Tại sao tôi phải giết ông ấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.02,Default,Reggie,0,0,0,,{I was in the casino until just now!}Lúc nãy tôi còn đang ở Casino mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:32.43,Default,Reggie,0,0,0,,{I'm not lying!}Tôi nói thật!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.93,Default,Reggie,0,0,0,,{I've lost almost 2,000 credits \Nsince this morning!}Tôi đã mất 2000 điểm từ sáng tới giờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.61,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{This footage is from the same time frame.}Đây là cảnh quay lại lúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.68,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{What's going on here?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:45.69,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{We can only deduce that the same man \Nwas in a different location at the same time.}Chỉ có thể kết luận rằng\N người giết nạn nhân là người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.16,Default,Cecile,0,0,0,,{I guess there was a murder?}Nghe nói có vụ giết người?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.32,Default,Cecile,0,0,0,,{That's terrifying!}Kinh khủng quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:54.23,Default,Worker1,0,0,0,,{All the staff are supposed to wait \Nin their cabins once this is done.}Tất cả nhân viên đều được yêu cầu ở trong phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.03,Default,Cecile (Giallon),0,0,0,,{Truly, so scary.}Sợ thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.82,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,{That woman is a witness.}Người phụ nữ kia là nhân chứng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:12.82,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{As a witness, you are obligated \Nto cooperate with our investiga—}Là nhân chứng, yêu cầu cô hợp tác điều tra--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.34,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Can you talk?}Cô nói được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.17,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{You saw the killer, right?}Cô đã thấy kẻ giết người nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.59,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{And they looked just like Cecile?}Và hắn y chang Cecile?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.63,Default,Worker1,0,0,0,,{Yeah... but it wasn't her.}Vâng... nhưng không phải cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:34.74,Default,Worker1,0,0,0,,{The face was the same, \Nbut that wasn't Cecile.}Khuôn mặt y đúc nhưng không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.51,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{What makes you think so?}Sao cô nghĩ thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.36,Default,Worker1,0,0,0,,{They smiled.}Hắn đã cười.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:39.70,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Smiled?}Cười?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.77,Default,Worker1,0,0,0,,{It was a really nasty smile.}Một nụ cười đáng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.37,Default,Worker1,0,0,0,,{That wasn't Cecile!}Đó không phải Cecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.76,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Yum!}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.96,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Shouldn't we be in our cabin?}Đáng ra phải ở trong phòng mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:00.44,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{It's back to the grind \Nas soon as we get to Earth.}Khi đến Trái Đất là phải đi làm khổ sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.04,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Like hell I'm just gonna stay \Nholed up in my cabin.}Nghĩ sao tôi chịu nhốt mình trong phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.31,Default,Aes,0,0,0,,{Should you two be out here?}Hai cô ở ngoài này ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.27,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Oh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.28,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{A...es? ...lice?}Aes? Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.85,Default,Aes,0,0,0,,{You met Alice?}Cô gặp Alice rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.72,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're Aes. You really are identical.}Aes à? Y chang luôn nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:19.11,Default,Aes,0,0,0,,{In what way? We're nothing alike.}Thế hả? Không giống lắm đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.04,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{So, what brings you here?}Vậy sao Aes lại đến đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:25.35,Default,Aes,0,0,0,,{We might not be able to leave our cabins \Nfor a while because of the murders,}Thì chúng ta không được rời khỏi phòng,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.57,Default,Aes,0,0,0,,{so Alice said to get some food.}nên Alice nói tôi đi mua thức ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.55,Default,Aes,0,0,0,,{She's such a slave-driver.}Chị ấy đúng là thích sai vặt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.80,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, the screening is canceled?}Bộ phim bị dừng là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.43,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{As I said, there's been an incident...}Có án mạng nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:38.09,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{Can you not see this big, strong Nean here?}Không nhìn thấy Nean to lớn mạnh mẽ này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.71,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{I've got a bodyguard!}Tôi có vệ sĩ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.47,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{That incident doesn't concern me!}Dăm ba cái án mạng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.18,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{I paid a lot of money to be here!}Tôi trả rất nhiều tiền cho chuyến đi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:48.75,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Yikes. Isn't that the old guy from the bus?}Lão già đợt xe bus đây mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.93,DefaultTop,Donald,0,0,0,,{Tch! Let's go, Huey.}Chậc, đi thôi Huey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:47.67,DefaultTop,Huey,0,0,0,,{Yes, sir.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.64,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{He's on the same ship?}Ông ta đi cùng tàu à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.83,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I'd rather see the murderer than him.}Thà gặp sát nhân còn hơn lão ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.76,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Aes, we can't send you back alone.}Aes, không nên quay về một mình lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.05,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Let's head back to the cabins together.}Cùng nhau về phòng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.72,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Tell Alice we said hi.}Gửi lời chào đến Alice nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.31,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{And don't leave your cabin.}Và đừng rời khỏi phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.84,Default,Aes,0,0,0,,{Sure. Later.}Ừ, gặp sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.17,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Wasn't expecting to see you \Nagain here, of all places.}Không ngờ lại gặp nhau ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:08.79,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Ugh.}Ặc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.67,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{You're with Aletheia, too?}Cô cũng bên Aletheia à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.80,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh... Uh...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:13.88,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{That's right!}Phải đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:17.82,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{We're right in the middle of our \Nwell-deserved, post-mission vacation!}Bọn tôi đang ở giữa kì nghỉ ngơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.09,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Got a problem?}Có vấn đề gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.35,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{There we go.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.05,Default,Naomi/Rouge,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.22,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,Naomi Orthmann.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.60,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{I'm taking you in under suspicion of murder.}Cô bị bắt vì tình nghi giết người.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.43,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh...}C-Cái...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.98,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{What the hell?!}Cái quái gì kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:39.03,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{It was the same at the \Nother murder scenes, too.}Ở hiện trường những vụ án khác cũng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:42.57,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{The video cuts off after this point, \Nso we can't track the killer.}Video bị cắt sau thời điểm này \Nnên không thể theo dấu hung thủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.77,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Two of the same person...}Hai người giống nhau...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.91,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{I guess it's what they call a doppelgänger.}Có lẽ đây là doppelgänger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.29,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{What is that?}Đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.71,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Never mind.}Không cần quan tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.29,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,Nói chung là để đảm bảo an tâm hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.36,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Sorry about this.}Nên là xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.43,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Two Naomis? Which one's the real one?}Có hai Naomi? Ai mới là thật?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:00.22,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{The one who was with you, obviously!}Người đang bên cạnh cô đây này!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.89,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Anyway, what kind of joke is this?}Cơ mà chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.06,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{To tell you the truth, I don't know, either.}Tôi cũng chả biết nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.85,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Then get these constraints off of me!}Vậy thì mau thả tôi ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.99,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{I can't trust anyone from Aletheia.}Tôi không thể tin ai từ Aletheia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.96,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{I made a deal with a certain someone}Lúc đó tôi đã thoả thuận với ai đó
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:16.05,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{under the condition that they'd \Ntell me who the red figure was,}với điều kiện cho biết tên màu đỏ đó là ai,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.95,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{but then they went AWOL on me.}nhưng cuối cùng lại bị nuốt lời.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:23.60,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{I've got a lot of questions to \Nask you once this is all over.}Sau chuyện này kết thúc tôi có nhiều thứ cần hỏi cô đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.37,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{"Find...}Hãy tìm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.53,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{me."}ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.98,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hell Giallon is on this ship.}Hell Giallon đang trên con tàu này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.40,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Yeah, of course.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.09,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{There's no doubt about it.}Chắc chắn luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:59.78,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{The series of incidents we've seen \Nare all part of Giallon's murder game.}Vụ án mạng liên tiếp đều là một phần kế hoạch của hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:02.53,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{And if we join the game, \Nwe're playing into his hands.}Và nếu tham gia, chúng ta sẽ rơi vào tay hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:08.54,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Our task is a top-secret mission that \Neven Chief Chau doesn't know about.}Nhiệm vụ của chúng ta là tuyệt mật\N đến mức giám đốc Chau cũng không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.66,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.80,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{We'll reach Earth soon.}Chúng ta sẽ đến Trái Đất sớm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.35,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Returning to Gene as quickly as possible, \Nwith as little involvement,}Quay trở lại với Gene ngay lập tức, \Nkhông gây ra náo loạn, im lặng mà biến mất,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.17,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{commotion, and exposure as possible, \Nis part of our mission.}sau đó tiếp tục nhiệm vụ càng sớm càng tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:21.26,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Our brilliant investigator from Ochrona \Nwill take care of everything.}Điều tra viên xuất sắc từ Ochrona sẽ lo mọi chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.70,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{You just stay in the cabin and behave.}Nói chung là cứ ở yên trong phòng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.58,DefaultItalics,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I don't want to!}Không chịu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:28.30,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I don't like you being suspected of murder,}Tôi không muốn Naomi bị tình nghi là kẻ giết người.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.28,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{and I'd hate myself for just \Nsitting around in this cabin}Và tôi ghét việc chỉ ngồi yên trong phòng
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.81,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{when he's about to kill someone!}mà nhìn ai đó bị giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:43.99,Default,Crew1,0,0,0,,{The body of a member of this ship's \Ncrew was found at the airport.}Thi thể của thành viên con tàu \Nnày được tìm thấy tại sân bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.08,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Who was it?}Ai đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:49.24,Default,Crew1,0,0,0,,{Uh... The murder victim was Rob Acres.}Nạn nhân của vụ giết người Rob Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:53.22,Default,Crew1,0,0,0,,{The terminal police on Mars \Nhave requested an investigation.}Cảnh sát trên sao Hoả đã yêu cầu điều tra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.25,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,{It must be some kind of mistake.}Có nhầm lẫn gì à.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:59.38,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,{He's been working as head of the \Ncabin crew since we departed.}Cậu ấy giữ chức trưởng nhóm \Ntừ khi chúng tôi khởi hành.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.67,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,{And I know he's not a ghost.}Và cậu ấy không phải hồn ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.55,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Right. I met him myself.}Phải nhỉ. Tôi cũng đã gặp anh ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.89,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{He was nearby when the first murder happened.}Anh ta ở gần hiện trường vụ đầu tiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.92,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Where is Acres?}Acres đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.36,DefaultItalics,AI,0,0,0,,{Rob Acres has not been located on this ship}Rob Acres đã được xác nhận có trên tàu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.44,DefaultItalics,AI,0,0,0,,{in the past two minutes and 32 seconds.}cách đây 2 phút 32 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:17.69,Default,Crew1,0,0,0,,{Maybe it really was a ghost?}Có khi là hồn ma thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.39,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{No way. Can't be.}Không thể nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.34,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{But if not that...}Nhưng nếu thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.22,DefaultItalics,Noid,0,0,0,,{Ash, look at this.}Ash, nhìn cái này xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.95,DefaultItalics,Noid,0,0,0,,{This is live footage.}Đây là video quay trực tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.65,DefaultItalics,Ash,0,0,0,,{Before the murder even happened this time?!}Trước khi bị giết mau làm gì đó đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.06,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,{Hey! Wait!}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.31,DefaultItalics,Ash,0,0,0,,Noid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.56,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Find out how much Rob Acres weighed \Nthe moment he boarded this ship!}Tìm hiểu cân nặng của Rob Acres khi hắn lên con tàu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:57.06,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{He's in the library disguised as me!}Hắn đang cải trang thành tôi trong thư viện.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:09.00,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Whoa, whoa! Wait! I'm the real one!}Khoan khoan! Hàng thật!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.19,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{See?}Thấy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.19,DefaultItalicsTop,Naomi (Bird),0,0,0,,{See?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:15.88,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Um...}À này...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.91,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Excuse me.}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.62,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Maybe she's already... you know... \Nand that's Giallon now?}Có khi bà ấy đã... ừ thì... Giallon ấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.36,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{It's not impossible. Should we kill her?}Không thể nào! Hay chúng ta nên giết bà ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.09,Default,Bianca,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's you two.}Hai cháu à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:34.60,Default,Bianca,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry. I turn off my hearing aid \Nwhen I want some quiet time.}Xin lỗi, mỗi khi yên ắng quá thì ta hay mơ màng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.82,Default,Bianca,0,0,0,,{It's my way of escaping my very loud husband.}Đây là cách ta thoát khỏi ông chồng phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.10,Default,Bianca,0,0,0,,{Our secret, okay?}Bí mật nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.92,Default,Rouge/Naomi,0,0,0,,{She's real.}Là hàng thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.03,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Not even this'll make me quit smoking.}Phải bỏ hút thuốc thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.49,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{Investigator Ash!}Điều tra viên Ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.95,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{There's been another murder!}Có vụ án!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.40,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,Phải thế chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.92,Default,Rouge (Giallon),0,0,0,,{Rouge just wants to play. She's at that age!}Rouge chỉ muốn vui chơi, bé đang đến tuổi lớn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.73,DefaultItalics,Noid,0,0,0,,{Ash! What happened?}Ash! Có chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.26,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Press down here.}Ấn chặt vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.74,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Rescue team to the library! Right now!}Đội giải cứu, mau đến thư viện ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.48,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Forget me. Just go.}Đi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.41,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Y-You...}C-Cô...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.66,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.29,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Wait! That's...}Khoan đã! Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.33,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Shithead...}Mẹ nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.87,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{This is why I hate Aletheia...}Đó là lý do mình ghét Aletheia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.25,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.46,Default,Rouge (Giallon),0,0,0,,{Hurry up and shoot!}Nhanh bắn đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.84,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Which one, though?!}Bắn ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.17,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Can't you figure that out?!}Không nhận ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.68,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Okay, time for a Rouge quiz! Fastest wins!}Vậy thì câu hỏi! Ai nhanh hơn thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.99,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,7+7÷7+7×7-7 bằng nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:15:59.85,Default,Rouge (Giallon),0,0,0,,{Fifty!}50!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.77,Default,Rouge (Giallon),0,0,0,,{Why?!}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.07,Default,Rouge (Giallon),0,0,0,,{How did you know?}Sao ngươi biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.24,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Rouge isn't that smart.}Rouge không khôn đến thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.66,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,7+7÷7+7×7-7 bằng nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.91,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Who cares?!}Ai quan tâm chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.29,Default,Rouge (Giallon),0,0,0,,{You're wide open!}Sơ hở!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.91,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{We're from Aletheia!}Bọn tôi đến từ Aletheia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.96,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{From this point, we're offering our \Nfull cooperation to this investigation!}Từ lúc này, yêu cầu hợp tác điều tra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.03,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.77,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Do you know the murderer's weight?}Cân nặng của hắn là bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.84,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{I was just looking it up \Non the investigator's orders.}Tôi đã làm theo yêu cầu của điều tra viên Ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.29,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hey, that old jerk did pretty good.}Lão già đó khá đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:41.68,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{Rob Acres, age 26, 182 centimeters.}Rob Acres, 26 tuổi, 1m82.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.48,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{When he boarded this ship, \Nhis weight was 82.2 kilograms.}Khi lên tàu hắn nặng 82.2kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:50.12,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Tập trung tất cả những ai nặng 82.2kg cho tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.55,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{You again!}Lại cô nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.62,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{One of you is the perpetrator \Nof these serial murders.}Trong các người có kẻ giết người.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.15,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Chúng tôi sẽ tiến hành điều tra--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.29,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I'm going to punch each one of you in turn!}Tôi sẽ đấm từng người một.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.29,Default,Suspects,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.42,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Wait, why?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.43,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{The one who can withstand \Nmy punch is Hell Giallon.}Kẻ nào chịu được một đấm\Ncủa tôi chính là Hell Giallon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.32,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{But the ones who can't will die.}Nhưng ai không chịu nổi là chết đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.54,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I can hold back }{\i1}{that}{\i0}{ much.}Cỡ đó thì tôi nương tay được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:15.36,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{This is the fastest way.}Đây là cách nhanh nhất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.43,Default,Guy1,0,0,0,,{Why do we have to get punched?}Sao tự nhiên lại phải ăn đấm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.01,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Pardon me!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.54,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{E-Enough of this! You're a woman!}Đủ rồi! Con nhỏ bạo lực!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.61,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{No one will ever want to marry—}Không ai dám đấm ta từ khi--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.46,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{You weigh 82.2 kilograms?}Cậu ta nặng 82.2kg?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:45.96,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,{That's the owner. The one that \Nweighs 82.2 kilograms is...}Là chủ. Con chó mới nặng 82.2kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.96,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{You're gonna punch Rubens?!}Khoan, cô tính đấm luôn thú hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.52,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Rubens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.98,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{That was cruel! I bet }{\i1}{you're}{\i0}{ the killer!}Độc ác quá! Cô mới là sát nhân!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:01.32,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{How could you kick a sweet dog like this?!}Sao cô có thể đá chú chó yêu dấu của tôi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.68,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,R-R-Rubens?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.98,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Quit trying to pass for a poor little dog,}Đừng có ra vẻ là con chó tội nghiệp nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:07.98,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Giallon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:11.12,Default,Rubens,0,0,0,,{You truly are a funny girl.}Cô đúng là thú vị mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.71,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{You're the funny one!}Ngươi mới là thằng hề đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:30.61,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Now... Come on over here!}Lại đây nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.43,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{Don't, Ash!}Đừng Ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:42.12,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I've wanted to kill you for a long time!}Ta đã luôn muốn giết cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.63,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{To kill someone just as strong as me,}Một kẻ mạnh mẽ giống ta,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:51.15,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{along with the thrill of knowing \NI could be killed, with my own hands!}cảm giác hồi hộp khi biết rằng mình có thể bị giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.57,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Ah...}A...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:58.03,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{My wish really is coming true!}Ước mơ của ta đã thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.24,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Say whatever you want!}Thích nói gì thì nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.99,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Your attacks are very simple.}Tấn công đơn giản quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.32,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I've seen every one of them coming!}Ta có thể đọc được hết
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.43,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I won't listen to a murderer!}Ta không nghe tên sát nhân đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:27.05,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Are you sure you should be \Nputting up that tough front?}Cô vẫn cố ra vẻ cứng rắn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:30.69,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{You'll never avenge your father that way.}Cô sẽ không thể trả thù cho cha mình theo cách đó đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.23,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?!}Ngươi nói nhảm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.81,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Exactly what I said.}Đúng như những gì ta nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.53,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{So it really was you!}Quả nhiên là ngươi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.03,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{You killed him!}Ngươi đã giết ông ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.70,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Bingo!}Chính xác!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:43.18,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I killed your father, Dr. Roy Junghardt,}Ta đã giết cha cô, tiến sĩ Roy Junghardt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:47.58,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{while in disguise as you!}trong khi cải trang thành cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.05,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Then take what you've got coming!}Vậy thì ta sẽ lấy lại tất cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:53.00,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{You're so quick to get all heated.}Nào nào, đừng nóng vội.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.48,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{That's a bad habit of yours!}Đó là thói xấu của cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:18.59,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,Adieu, Rouge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:24.99,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,{A filthy shooting star \Nis falling right into Hell.}Một ngôi sao băng bẩn thỉu đang rơi xuống địa ngục.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.32,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,{Perfect.}Hoàn hảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.84,Default,Comms,0,0,0,,{Captain.}Đội trưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.49,Default,Comms,0,0,0,,{The patrol craft has given \Norders to stop the ship.}Tàu tuần tra đã ra lệnh dừng lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.71,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Darn it! I've been looking for you!}Thiệt tình! Tôi tìm cô mãi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.21,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Good work.}Làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.56,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Who are they?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.10,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Ochrona's Artificial Life \NInspection Department.}Phòng kiểm tra sự sống nhân tạo của Ochrona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:09.59,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.66,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Rouge Redstar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:18.43,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{You are under arrest for violating article 5,\Nclause 9 of the Use of Artificial Life Code.}Cô bị bắt vì vi phạm điều 5 khoản 9\N bộ luật Sự dụng sự sống nhân tạo.
